*Glupi* ljudi često prave greške. (Stupid people often make mistakes.)

Ona je rekla da je *glup* kad je pogrešila. (She said she was stupid when she made a mistake.)

Oni su ponašali *glupo* kada su se prepirali. (They acted stupidly when they argued.)

Oni ne znaju da rade *gluposti*. (They don't know how to do stupid things.)

Razmislite pre nego što uradite nešto *glupo*. (Think before you do something stupid.)